From 0ac810ec37beba059f8ba20b45c3bbd8a76ca266 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jingsheng Yan <yanjingsheng@sjtu.edu.cn>
Date: Mon, 31 Mar 2025 14:44:58 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add futex support and related system calls

- Introduced futex mechanism for thread synchronization, including sys_futex, sys_futex_wait, sys_futex_wake, and sys_futex_requeue.
- Added futex_entry structure and associated functions for managing waiters.
- Updated notification handling to support futex operations.
- Enhanced cap_group and thread structures to include futex-related fields.
- Implemented syscall interface for setting thread ID addresses.
- Updated CMake configuration to accommodate new syscall definitions.
